Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝… 謹遵約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還這麼早就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天受過傷的 應該多睡會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜我很結實的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是身體上 其實還有些心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 被「古物」所襲擊的村裡的人們 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」臨死前所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「汝… 謹遵約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次碰到「古物」開口說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且… 那個「汝」指的又是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「約定」到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們對於小夜你來說是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是應當消滅的物件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被「古物」的花言巧語所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個… 好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和平時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬兒鳴叫著 雲兒千姿百態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真的… 真的… 很舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個… 好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是一如既往地安穩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡很平靜並溫柔的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人之前一臉嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我受傷的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須變得更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也一如既往的相當悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 天氣倒是很溫和的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像發生過什麼事情一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是說麵包店的老闆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 那家店到現在還沒開門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果似乎說是老闆他還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上路過那邊的時候從那些本想去買麵包的人那邊聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連巡警都特地來「Guimauve」通知大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察應該也到處搜尋過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過好像還沒找到在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是不是很像…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭倦了這樣的地方所以離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都成年人了還可以說成是離家出走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然還能怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗它…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫醫生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對… 在這之前得先去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你爬到樹上去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是追上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追小狗… 雖然不確定到底是不是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過體形非常的小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼追狗要爬到樹上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那只小狗很輕盈地就跳上樹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不應該是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 要是再不快點吃飯的話 午休就要結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊 我差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學你呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其吃飯還不如去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 肚子要是餓的話 心情也是會悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話 你之前也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是這種樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人 還真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學笑起來真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦 這是文人先生做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生是「Cafe Guimauve」的老闆 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽到有人說文人先生做的料理好吃我就會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這個叫文人的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜她去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常… 非常地喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生既溫柔 料理又很拿手 並且一直聽我傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是溫柔 料理拿手 聽你傾訴就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的算是喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被問到這種事情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是做了什麼讓時真同學生氣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我覺得不是這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他一臉凝重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也有他自己的各種狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟還太年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然喝了文人先生的咖啡就會平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是為小夜特製的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是「Guimauve」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 因為小夜是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎麼的 一下子走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事的話就說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是多麼微小的事情也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變一個人的感情是很困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那是什麼東西 只要是銘刻於內心深處的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來最困難的是「憎惡」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然人們常常說「憎惡是無法持續的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這並不意味著消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隱藏在表面察覺不到的地方 完整地殘留著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 借由一個微小的契機 再次原形畢露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 如果無法消除這棘手的「憎惡」 又該怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了迸發出與其同等強烈的感情之外也別無他法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與「憎惡」同等強烈的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那就是「愛情」和「信賴」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快逃離這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 挺住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和描述的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！ 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汝想要消滅吾等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝連戰鬥方式都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個 操縱著它們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等也是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層操縱著下層
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了想要操縱一切而再次展開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也是有無法操縱的東西存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹遵約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約…定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所指的是「主事鬼面」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主事鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等為自己的利益而吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要妨礙吾等 就連汝等也一起吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有戰鬥是我必須要貫徹到底的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小夜我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」已經消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個什麼樣的「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說和我們一樣的「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 還說了… 要謹遵約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求衛奈奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求衛諾諾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲到了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了 更衣同學的點名已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 點名還沒有完全結束 就不算你遲到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是個好天氣 也沒出什麼騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺又是一個既平靜又安穩的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育課改上自習課了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來說說鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成說鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 自習課可不是用來玩這個的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長 難道你害怕恐怖的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪… 哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學不能逃跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家要一起說鬼故事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「久別重逢」
